(## Architecture \(how requests flow\)) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Controller layer \(controller/*Controller.java\): defines /api/... endpoints, validates inputs) Tj
0 -12 Td
(\(@Valid\), and delegates to services.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Service layer \(service/* + service/impl/*Impl.java\): business logic, orchestration, paging) Tj
0 -12 Td
(sanitization, and error rules.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Repository layer \(repository/*Repository.java\): Spring Data JPA interfaces for) Tj
0 -12 Td
(persistence/querying.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Entities \(entity/*.java\): JPA mappings to the Sakila schema.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- DTOs \(dto/\): request/response models and validation constraints.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Mappers \(mapper/*Mapper.java\): conversions between entities and DTOs.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(- Exception handling \(exception/*\): centralized error mapping to structured JSON.) Tj
